{"data":[{"id":561834130,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9efc5b1f477eb834c48922bf19412774","url_token":"zuo-shou-guang-yin-55","name":"左手光阴","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a94fb2fc149d2d77540beae8cf97d5d4_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a94fb2fc149d2d77540beae8cf97d5d4_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9efc5b1f477eb834c48922bf19412774","user_type":"people","headline":"心如死灰","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":6,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561834130","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546005975,"updated_time":1546005975,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":23,"comment_count":6,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e有一天我去开会，到场的有上万人，我问在座的每一位同学小朋友 ，我这个《关于哥德巴赫猜想的证明》一次都没有看过的请举手，没有一个人举手，什么叫国际数学家啊？\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 还看过我们现在的一些论文，哥德巴赫和欧拉都谈起恋爱来了，哥德巴赫叫欧拉叫拉拉，欧拉叫哥德巴赫叫赫赫，几何不分质素颠倒，有意思吗？甚至把哥德巴赫变成数学史上的情种，这是非常要不得的，那不是我们搞数学猜想的要做的事情。\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 数学文化浓缩起来就是哥德巴赫文化，哥德巴赫文化就是高中生精神，读懂了我就读懂了整个数学界。\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 我还看过哪个论文里，哥德巴赫猜想是这么推导的，一点精气神都没有，那不成了无效证明。\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 有位民科跟我说啦，他说高中生先生啊，你回去跟我们的学生讲，数学上古今中外不缺可歌可泣的爱情故事，请给哥德巴赫留下一片爱情的净土。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我就一直讲，戏说不是胡说，哥猜不是乱猜。你用高等数学来证明哥德巴赫猜想是要向本国数学界谢罪的。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 刚才有个小朋友就问啦，他说高中生叔叔，哥德巴赫猜想在证明的时候有几个数论知识啊。\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 去清北讲课的时候有个收费人员把我拦了下来，看了我的教师资格证，说：您这证书是假的吧？我说，是真的。他又说：您不是姓哥吗？\u003cbr\u003e \u003cbr\u003e 一个数学领域没有自己的猜想是可怕的，有了猜想却不去证明是可悲的，如果有高中生证明出来却不被承认是可耻的。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 我的哥德巴赫猜想，在陈景润面前，pia，对面门里里面出来个老头，我本子一摔，钢笔一扔，上下一打量，哦这是个没证明出哥德巴赫猜想的数学家，太菜！就这么简单，很难再看出别的情感，如果对面门里出来了一个老头，我一看哇这个老头太帅气啦，是不是可以跟我发展一段基情，我是做不出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e苦练初等数学，笑证三大猜想。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbr\u003e 我的新书《听高中生说哥德巴赫猜想》、《高中生品数论》、《哥德巴赫猜想（圣诞节珍藏版）》、自传《天才高中生》已出版，两手翻花，文理百家齐炸，请大家多多支持！\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"有一天我去开会，到场的有上万人，我问在座的每一位同学小朋友 ，我这个《关于哥德巴赫猜想的证明》一次都没有看过的请举手，没有一个人举手，什么叫国际数学家啊？ 还看过我们现在的一些论文，哥德巴赫和欧拉都谈起恋爱来了，哥德巴赫叫欧拉叫拉拉，欧拉叫…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=152\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotati